quoteText: Do Not Track (DNT) is an optional browser setting that allows you to express your preferences regarding tracking by advertisers and other third-parties.  We do not respond to DNT signals.
title: This service ignores the Do Not Track (DNT) header and tracks users anyway even if they set this header.
